les and Females receiving a bonus payment  96% of Females received a Bonus versus 91% of Males  Proportion of Males and Females in each pay quartile   Upper Quartile = 90% Male and 10% Female  Upper Middle Quartile = 83% Male and 17% Female  Lower Middle Quartile = 99% Male and 1% Female  Lower Quartile = 93% Male and 7% Female            Relevant Experience             B4RN Community Projects  FIBREFLOW™ SOLUTION  North West England, UK         Emtelle supply FibreFlow™ solution to Broadband for the Rural North Ltd to enable remote rural communities to be connected to a fibre optic broadband network.   Read more >           Olympics Stadium  FIBRE & POWER CABLE DUCTS  London, England         Emtelle is proud to have been involved with the London Olympic Stadium construction project, being chosen to supply the Distribution Network Operator (DNO) for London, EDF Energy, for the ambitious project.   Read more >           GOTTHARD BASE TUNNEL  Microduct installation         Emtelle provided thousands of kilometres of its FibreFlow™ Microduct solution to the transalpine Swiss Railway Gotthard Base Tunnel.   Read more >                  Engage Emtelle               Phone         Email         Ask An Emtelle Expert         Request a Callback         Request I&M; Manual           LATEST FROM EMTELLE  LATEST             NEWS      NEWSLETTER SIGN UP              Emtelle Robust Fiber Certification      Emtelle Completes Powerprotect+ Data Centre Portfolio with Launch of New End-to-End Solution      Emtelle Launches Indoor Pre-Connectorised Fibre Microduct System      B4RN Show-Tell Day #12        Emtelle Robust Fiber Certification    Read more >      Emtelle Completes Powerprotect+ Data Centre Portfolio with Launch of New End-to-End Solution    Read more >      Emtelle Launches Indoor Pre-Connectorised Fibre Microduct System    Read more >      B4RN Show-Tell Day #12    Read more >        NEWSLETTER SIGN UP    Get all the latest Emtelle information    *   Comments This field 